    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Can you instead add event listeners to the elements you want: \r\n\r\n```js\r\ndocument.querySelectorAll('.click-analytics').forEach(element =>\r\n  element.addEventListener('click', e => {\r\n    let correct_position = 1 + parseInt(e.target.getAttribute('data-position'));\r\n    window.aa('click', {\r\n      objectID: e.target.getAttribute('data-objectid'),\r\n      position: correct_position,\r\n    });\r\n    console.log(e.target.getAttribute('data-objectid'));\r\n  })\r\n);\r\n\r\ndocument.querySelectorAll('.conversion-analytics').forEach(element =>\r\n  element.addEventListener('click', e => {\r\n    window.aa('conversion', {\r\n      objectID: e.target.getAttribute('data-objectid'),\r\n    });\r\n    console.log(e.target.getAttribute('data-objectid'));\r\n  })\r\n);\r\n```",
